               <note xml:id="d2e6173" n="1"> On this form see vol 1, Benjamin (1) B/M, p.
                            82.</note>
               <note xml:id="d2e6180" n="2"> Described in the text – <span xml:lang="gr"></span> (in Tiberias). On
